SUMMARY OF DATA CARDS FOR NASA/AMES WING-BODY PROGRAM
  1  This series of configurations studied the characteristics of                                                                        
  2  cranked leading edge planforms.                                                                                                     
  3  A wind tunnel test case reported in NASA TN D-4211                                                                                  
  4                                                                                                                                      
  5  CRANKED WING-BODY FROM TN D-4211                                                                                                    
  6   &BODY  LNOSE=5.688, LBODY=14.216, RADIUS=0.4375,                                                                                   
  7          NB=3, NROWS=10, XSTART=4.113,                                                                                               
  8          SREF=21.75, CBAR=4.218, REFMOM=9.928, OC=4,                                                                                 
  9          MACH=0.5,                                                                                                                   
 10   &END                                                                                                                               
 11   &WING  ROOTLE=4.113, ROOTTE=13.216, ROOTY=0.4375,                                                                                  
 12          TIPLE=9.533, TIPTE=13.216, TIPY=1.2,                                                                                        
 13          TCROOT=0.03, TCTIP=0.03,                                                                                                    
 14          ROWS=10, COLS=4,                                                                                                            
 15   &END                                                                                                                               
 16   &WING  ROOTLE=9.533,ROOTY=1.2,                                                                                                     
 17          TIPLE=12.616, TIPY=2.98,                                                                                                    
 18   &END                                                                                                                               
 19   &AERO  CASE=2,                                                                                                                     
 20   &END                                                                                                                               
 21   &INCR  DELTA=2,                                                                                                                    
 22   &END                                                                                                                               
 23  ... notice that we can change OC in the middle of the aero runs                                                                     
 24  ... so we don't get the full output for alpha=4 and 6                                                                               
 25   &INCR  OC=1,&END                                                                                                                   
 26   &INCR  &END                                                                                                                        
 27                                                                                                                                      
END OF DATA CARDS 



